params.markdown:
This dashboard is designed to provide focused visibility into logon and logoff activities using the Security data stream.

It highlights the top 10 group membership logons by account name, visualizes group membership events by logon type and user, and presents detailed insights into trust direction filtering. The dashboard also tracks workstation lock events across users, security IDs, and account domains to support monitoring of authentication patterns and identification of unusual behavior.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/system/overview)**
